    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This bug is much trickier because this bug is related to the bug in React Native (https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/6552). Switching from `onContentSizeChange` to `onChange` solves one problem, but leads to another — `onChange` fires only when a user enters text via a keyboard thus the suggested fix leads to problems with emoji picker and pasting text to the input.\r\n\r\nThe best thing we can do is to\r\n1) Change label from `beginner` to `intermediate` because this task means fixing React Native, not our code;\r\n2) Postpone it a bit and let @viebel work on another task instead.\r\n\r\nThanks for your job, @viebel, but unfortunately this task is not that easy as it sounds and looks.",
